    {# ── INTRO / HISTORY ── #}
    <section class="cs-about-intro">
      <div class="cs-about-intro__text">
        <h2 class="cs-section-label">Our Story</h2>
        <p>
          Founded in <strong>1972</strong>, the Department of Computer Science at Stellenbosch University has grown into one of the leading
          computer science research and education institutions in Africa. In a strategic restructuring, the department merged with
          Mathematics and Applied Mathematics to form the <strong>Computer Science Division</strong> within the Department of Mathematical
          Sciences — creating a unique interdisciplinary hub where computation meets rigorous mathematics.
        </p>
        <p>
          From our home on the oak-lined campus of Stellenbosch, we have produced generations of researchers, entrepreneurs,
          and industry leaders who contribute to South Africa's growing technology ecosystem and beyond.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-about-intro__timeline">
        <div class="cs-timeline-item">
          <span class="cs-timeline-item__year">1972</span>
          <span class="cs-timeline-item__text">Department founded at Stellenbosch University</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-timeline-item">
          <span class="cs-timeline-item__year">1990</span>
          <span class="cs-timeline-item__text">Software verification research group established</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-timeline-item">
          <span class="cs-timeline-item__year">2005</span>
          <span class="cs-timeline-item__text">Machine Learning & AI group launched</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-timeline-item">
          <span class="cs-timeline-item__year">2018</span>
          <span class="cs-timeline-item__text">Merger into Department of Mathematical Sciences</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-timeline-item">
          <span class="cs-timeline-item__year">Today</span>
          <span class="cs-timeline-item__text">11 faculty, 7 research groups, 50+ postgraduates</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

